title: Bright Main Floor Unit Available Sept. 1, Large Bedroom w/Walk-in, A/C
posting_body: ['Bright Main Floor Unit Available September 1 in Cathedral Hill, Large Bedroom w/Walk-in Closet', 'Property Address', '385 Ashland Ave - #C | St. Paul, MN 55102', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'With occupied units, we are only able to do a showing after an application is approved.', ' To apply, go to <URL>', 'Each adult would apply and upload last two pay statements and proof of other income.', 'Main floor unit available September 1 in 5 unit building in Cathedral Hill.', ' Large bright living room with a built-in a/c unit and large windows overlooking the front of the property.', 'The bedroom is large and has a walk-in closet and additional shelving outside the bedroom.', ' The kitchen is bright with window on two sides and has space for a small dining table.', " There's a full bathroom off the living room with lots of storage.", "There's shared laundry downstairs.", "There's just street parking at this building.", 'This is in the sought after Cathedral Hill neighborhood in St. Paul.', 'Walking distance to WA Frost, The Gnome, Red Cow and Moscow on the Hill.', 'Cats are okay with a $25/month pet fee per.', 'Sorry no dogs.', '$50 application fee per adult', 'We check income (gross household income must be at least 3 times rent), credit (must be 600+), criminal and rental history', 'Rent includes gas (heat), water & trash', 'Call Dakota at', 'show contact info', 'for more information', 'Agent: Dakota DeHaven', 'BROKER: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 780', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,112.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,112.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
